The renowned presenter Jessica Cediel does not stop falling in love with her millions of followers with her beauty and sensuality, this time she left them stunned with a fiery publication in which she appears wearing a pronounced cleavage.
But it was not only the cleavage and its voluptuous breasts that seduced Instagram users, but also its provocative mouth pointing out that their kisses "taste like vanilla", a confession that unleashed euphoria and hundreds of comments in the publication.
